headline: Lockheed Martin's Arm Secures a Contract to Support Sonar Systems
summary: LMT's unit secures a $15.2 million modification contract to procure hardware for supporting sonar systems.

headline: AAR & Cebu Pacific Ink a Component Repair Contract for A320 Fleet
summary: AIR inks a deal to offer Cebu Pacific Air nacelle MRO services. The work is likely to be executed in Chonburi, Thailand.
